  "text": "Children's anxiety can sometimes turn to a predicament if disregarded by family, school, or even the society and can lead to complications in adulthood. Therefore, early diagnosis and treatment is highly important [CITATION_1] . This study aimed to assess the effect of the communication skills training of mothers using multimedia software program in reducing the anxiety level of first-grade students in a residential complex in Tehran.",
